[src:asymptotic-analysis/watson-s-lemma] as $x\to \infty$ , where the infinite series is interpreted as an asymptotic expansion of the integral in question.
[src:asymptotic-analysis/watson-s-lemma] which is now amenable to the use of Watson's lemma.
